327
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:45,380
Why can't he?

328
00:18:47,490 --> 00:18:49,520
His profession is a little special.

329
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:50,540
It's not up to him

330
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,250
