331
00:18:53,910 --> 00:18:55,290
You're talking about Liang Mu Ze, right?

332
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:58,590
It doesn't matter who it is.

333
00:18:58,850 --> 00:19:00,230
I just want to know,

334
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,660
