of holding a surgery knife.

365
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:06,780
So,

366
00:20:07,210 --> 00:20:08,290
I've endured 27 years

367
00:20:08,370 --> 00:20:09,670
of hardship.

368
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:11,650
There's no way I could give up
my career

369
