370
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:16,040
However,

371
00:20:16,130 --> 00:20:17,820
I've given it serious thought.

372
00:20:18,170 --> 00:20:19,750
To be like Professor Lin Qiao Zhi,

373
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,340
